---
import ServiceLayout from '../../../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout
  title="Quantum Verification Services"
  description="Comprehensive testing and validation services for quantum computing systems and algorithms"
>
  <div class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Ensuring Quantum Computing Excellence</h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">
      Our quantum verification services provide rigorous testing and validation frameworks to ensure the reliability, accuracy, and efficiency of quantum computing implementations. We combine advanced testing methodologies with deep quantum expertise to deliver comprehensive verification solutions.
    </p>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Verification Methodology</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600 mr-2 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold">Static Analysis</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Quantum circuit validation and optimization verification</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600 mr-2 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold">Dynamic Testing</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Runtime behavior analysis and performance testing</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600 mr-2 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold">Formal Verification</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Mathematical proof of correctness for quantum algorithms</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Quality Assurance</h3>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-purple-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
              <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-purple-600">99%</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold">Accuracy Rate</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">In quantum algorithm verification</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-purple-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
              <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-purple-600">100x</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold">Faster Testing</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Compared to traditional methods</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-purple-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
              <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-purple-600">24/7</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold">Monitoring</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Continuous verification and validation</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-100 to-indigo-100 p-8 rounded-lg mb-12">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6">Verification Framework</h3>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-purple-600 mb-3">Circuit Validation</h4>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
            <li>• Gate-level verification</li>
            <li>• Quantum state analysis</li>
            <li>• Error rate assessment</li>
            <li>• Optimization validation</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-purple-600 mb-3">Performance Testing</h4>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
            <li>• Execution time analysis</li>
            <li>• Resource utilization</li>
            <li>• Scalability testing</li>
            <li>• Benchmark comparisons</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-purple-600 mb-3">Result Validation</h4>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
            <li>• Output verification</li>
            <li>• Statistical analysis</li>
            <li>• Error correction</li>
            <li>• Consistency checks</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md mb-12">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6">Case Study: Financial Algorithm Verification</h3>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-purple-600 mb-3">Challenge</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            A leading financial institution needed to verify the accuracy of their quantum portfolio optimization algorithm.
          </p>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-purple-600 mb-3">Solution</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            We implemented our comprehensive verification framework to validate the algorithm's correctness and performance.
          </p>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-purple-600 mb-3">Results</h4>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
            <li>• 99.9% accuracy in portfolio optimization</li>
            <li>• 60% reduction in verification time</li>
            <li>• Identified and resolved 3 critical edge cases</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-purple-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
          <h4 class="font-semibold mb-4">Verification Process</h4>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            {[
              "Initial assessment and planning",
              "Static analysis of quantum circuits",
              "Dynamic testing with sample data",
              "Performance optimization",
              "Final validation and documentation"
            ].map((step, index) => (
              <div class="flex items-center">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-purple-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
                  {index + 1}
                </div>
                <p class="text-gray-700">{step}</p>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-purple-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Ensure Your Quantum Success</h2>
    <p class="mb-6">Ready to verify your quantum computing implementation? Contact us to discuss how our verification services can help ensure the reliability and efficiency of your quantum solutions.</p>
    <div class="flex gap-4">
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-purple-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-purple-700 transition-colors">
        Schedule a Consultation
      </a>
      <a href="/services/quantum/solutions" class="inline-block bg-white text-purple-600 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-purple-50 transition-colors">
        Explore Industry Solutions
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</ServiceLayout>